{
  "texts": [
    "A final point raised by both MOSACAT and the Council concerns the extent to which data centres and lithium extraction encompasses a threat to the well-being and even survival of communities.",
    "In the case of MOSACAT, there are concerns that the Google data centre could end up leaving the community without access to pipeline water.",
    "This situation generates frustration for MOSACAT.",
    "As one of them expressed to me:",
    "It is sad to see that you are worth nothing."
  ]
}